title: T3/T9 Boxing Complete Set - all psa graded
author: t206kid

posts.post_title: T3/T9 Boxing Complete Set - all psa graded
posts.post_content:
Complete boxing set of 26 cards.  Average grade is right at a 2, all PSA graded.  Jack Johnson is a 1 and pictured.  These boxing cards are tough to find because it costs $100+ each to grade them.  Great to accompany a T3 set.  Not looking to break up at this time.

$8,500 FF
